OL,3,CGovernment to crackdown on child
OL,4,Cbenefit claims from abroad
OL,6,FThe Government has launched a
OL,7,Fcrackdown on people who continue to
OL,8,Fclaim child benefit after they have
OL,9,Fleft the UK in a bid to save #350
OL,10,Fmillion over the next five years.
OL,12,FIt said that "tens of thousands" of
OL,13,Fclaimants who incorrectly claim after
OL,14,Fleaving the UK will be stripped of the
OL,15,Fbenefits.
OL,17,FPeople who leave the UK for more than
OL,18,Feight weeks are not eligible for the
OL,19,Fbenefit, unless under exceptional
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
