OL,3,CGovernment to crackdown on child
OL,4,Cbenefit claims from abroad
OL,6,FThe clampdown comes after a successful
OL,7,Ftrial in which 15 investigators
OL,8,Fremoved 2,600 people from the system
OL,9,Fwho continued to claim child benefits
OL,10,Fabroad, saving #17 million over the
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FMinisters announced a specialist team
OL,14,Fscouring international travel data and
OL,15,F200,000 child benefit records to find
OL,16,Fwrongful payments will be
OL,17,Fsignificantly expanded to send a
OL,18,F"clear warning to those trying to scam
OL,19,Fthe system".
