OL,3,CGovernment to crackdown on child
OL,4,Cbenefit claims from abroad
OL,6,FThe team will grow to more than 200
OL,7,Finvestigators from next month.
OL,9,FCabinet Office minister Georgia Gould
OL,10,Fsaid: "This government is putting a
OL,11,Fstop to people claiming benefits when
OL,12,Fthey aren't eligible to do so.
OL,14,F"From September, we'll have ten times
OL,15,Fas many investigators saving hundreds
OL,16,Fof millions of pounds of taxpayer's
OL,17,Fmoney.
OL,19,F"If you're claiming benefits you're
OL,20,Fnot entitled to, your time is up."
