OL,6,FChild benefit is one of the most
OL,7,Fwidely accessed benefits in the UK
OL,8,Fpaid to more than 6.9 million families
OL,9,Fand supporting 11.9 million children.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe government hopes the crackdown
OL,17,Fwill increase awareness about the
OL,18,Fbenefit rules to avoid those who
OL,19,Fcontinue to claim the benefit abroad
OL,20,Fby mistake.
