OL,3,CGovernment to crackdown on child
OL,4,Cbenefit claims from abroad
OL,6,FLabour previously faced criticism
OL,7,Frelating to child benefits after
OL,8,Fformer Prime Minister and Labour
OL,9,FChancellor Gordon Brown put pressure
OL,10,Fon the government to scrap the two-
OL,11,Fchild benefit cap, describing rising
OL,12,Fchild poverty in the UK as a "cancer
OL,13,Fin our society".
OL,15,FThe former political heavyweight has
OL,16,Fcalled on Chancellor Rachel Reeves to
OL,17,Fend the controversial policy that
OL,18,Festimated to affect 1.5 million
OL,19,Fchildren across the country.
